---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContactForm from '../../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Digital Marketing for Barber Shops &#8212; Sydney"
  description="SNAV Marketing helps Sydney barber shops get fully booked with Instagram, Facebook Ads, Google Maps optimisation and booking system integrations."
  canonical="/industries/barber-shops"
>
  <section class="industry-hero">
    <div class="container-lg">
      <p class="eyebrow">Industry Specialists</p>
      <div class="hero-icon">💈</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Keep Every Chair Full,<br />Every Day of the Week</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Great cuts deserve great marketing. SNAV helps Sydney barber shops build packed appointment books with social media that stops the scroll and local ads that bring new clients through the door.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Fill My Appointment Book</a>
        <a href="/portfolio" class="btn-secondary">See Our Results</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-lg two-col">
      <div>
        <h2 class="h2">Your Shop Deserves to Be Packed &#8212; Not Quiet on Tuesdays</h2>
        <p class="body-text">Word of mouth built your reputation. But it can't fill the gaps on quiet afternoons or attract new clients when they move into the suburb. That's where SNAV comes in.</p>
        <p class="body-text">We specialise in marketing for barber shops across Sydney &#8212; from Newtown to the Northern Beaches. We know what makes people choose a new barber: great photos, authentic reviews, easy booking and a vibe that matches theirs. We build marketing that communicates all of that.</p>

        <h3 class="h3">What We Do for Barber Shops</h3>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Instagram content strategy &#8212; transformation photos, Reels, Stories</li>
          <li>Facebook and Instagram Ads targeting your local suburbs</li>
          <li>Google Maps & SEO &#8212; "barber near me" searches</li>
          <li>Google review generation campaigns</li>
          <li>Online booking integration (Booksy, Square Appointments, etc.)</li>
          <li>Loyalty campaign ideas and promotions</li>
          <li>Website refresh or new site with online booking</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="results-col">
        <h3 style="color:white; font-size:1.125rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Real Results</h3>
        <div class="result-card">
          <span class="result-stat">100%</span>
          <span class="result-label">Chair occupancy achieved</span>
          <span class="result-client">J-Cuts, Surry Hills &#8212; (from 60% in 6 weeks)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="result-card">
          <span class="result-stat">+280%</span>
          <span class="result-label">Instagram followers in 3 months</span>
          <span class="result-client">The Fade Factory, Marrickville</span>
        </div>
        <div class="result-card">
          <span class="result-stat">2 wks</span>
          <span class="result-label">Advance booking wait time</span>
          <span class="result-client">King's Cuts, Bondi Junction</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad" style="background: var(--bg-alt);">
    <div class="container-lg">
      <h2 class="h2 text-center">Why Barber Shop Marketing Is Different</h2>
      <p class="body-text text-center" style="max-width:640px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;">
        Barber shops are personal. Clients are loyal &#8212; but they need a reason to try you first. Here's how we crack that.
      </p>
      <div class="what-grid">
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">??</span>
          <h3>Visual-First Content</h3>
          <p>We help you create or guide you to capture transformation content that performs on Instagram and TikTok &#8212; the platforms where people discover new barbers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">??</span>
          <h3>Hyper-Local Ad Targeting</h3>
          <p>We target specific suburbs around your shop &#8212; so your ads reach people within walking or driving distance who are actively looking for a new barber.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">?</span>
          <h3>Google Review Strategy</h3>
          <p>We automate review requests after each appointment &#8212; building your Google rating so you dominate "barber near me" searches in your area.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">??</span>
          <h3>Fill the Quiet Slots</h3>
          <p>Targeted promotions for Tuesday and Wednesday afternoons, last-minute social posts and SMS campaigns to your existing client list fill the gaps.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">??</span>
          <h3>Booking System Integration</h3>
          <p>We connect your marketing directly to your booking platform &#8212; so every ad click, Instagram Story swipe-up and Google search ends in an appointment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">??</span>
          <h3>Community Building</h3>
          <p>We manage your DMs and comments to build genuine relationships with followers &#8212; turning casual likers into regular clients.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad cta-section">
    <div class="container-lg cta-inner">
      <div>
        <h2 class="cta-heading">Ready to Fill Your Chair?</h2>
        <p class="cta-sub">Get a free social media and local SEO audit of your barbershop. We'll show you exactly what's holding back new clients &#8212; and how we'd fix it.</p>
        <ul class="cta-list">
          <li>? Sydney specialists &#8212; we know your market</li>
          <li>? Content strategy + paid ads + SEO</li>
          <li>&#10003; No lock-in contracts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-form">
        <ContactForm />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .industry-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A5F 0%, #152b47 100%); padding: 5rem 0; text-align: center; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #FF6B35; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .hero-icon { font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .hero-title { font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.25rem); font-weight: 900; color: white; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #94afc7; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
  .hero-ctas { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; }

  .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }

  .h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .h3 { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-heading); margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .body-text { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-body); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .text-center { text-align: center; }

  .service-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-body); }
  .service-list li::before { content: '\2192 '; color: #FF6B35; font-weight: 700; }

  .results-col { background: #1E3A5F; border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .result-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .result-stat { display: block; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: #FF6B35; line-height: 1; }
  .result-label { display: block; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin: 0.25rem 0; }
  .result-client { display: block; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #7a9bbf; }

  .what-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
  @media (min-width: 640px)  { .what-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .what-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }

  .what-card { background: var(--surface-card); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.06); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .what-icon { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .what-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .what-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-muted); }

  .cta-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35 0%, #e55a24 100%); }
  .cta-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .cta-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
  .cta-heading { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 800; color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-sub { font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .cta-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.625rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; }
  .cta-form { background: var(--surface-card); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.2); }
</style>

